      "text": "<p>Element vašeg <code>div</code> ispod elementa <code>header</code> mora imati klasu od <code>flex-container</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const divELBelowHeader = document.querySelector('header + div');\nassert.equal(divELBelowHeader.className, 'flex-container');"
    },
